                <h1>Duke alumni weekend recap: Sue Gordon to resign, Andrew McCabe sues Trump administration</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/a15c5498-d122-4442-bb06-ad5287431e95.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;Two&#x20;Duke&#x20;alumni&#x20;were&#x20;once&#x20;top&#x20;national&#x20;security&#x20;officials&#x3A;&#x20;Sue&#x20;Gordon&#x20;&#x28;left&#x29;&#x20;and&#x20;Andrew&#x20;McCabe&#x20;&#x28;right&#x29;.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>Two Duke alumni were once top national security officials: Sue Gordon (left) and Andrew McCabe (right).</p>

